    "# üß† An√°lisis No Supervisado con K-Means (EA3 ‚Äì Machine Learning)\n",
    "\n",
    "Este notebook implementa el algoritmo **K-Means Clustering** para identificar segmentos homog√©neos \n",
    "de clientes dentro del dataset de scoring crediticio. \n",
    "\n",
    "El objetivo es complementar el modelo supervisado principal mediante:\n",
    "- Identificaci√≥n de patrones o subpoblaciones relevantes.\n",
    "- Detecci√≥n de comportamientos diferenciados.\n",
    "- An√°lisis de posibles grupos con riesgo crediticio similar.\n",
    "\n",
    "El an√°lisis se realiza utilizando exclusivamente el **conjunto de entrenamiento**, tal como indica la pauta.\n"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "inertia = []\n",
    "K_range = range(1, 11)\n",
    "\n",
    "for k in K_range:\n",
    "    km = KMeans(n_clusters=k, random_state=42)\n",
    "    km.fit(X_sample)\n",
    "    inertia.append(km.inertia_)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8,5))\n",
    "plt.plot(K_range, inertia, marker=\"o\")\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"N√∫mero de clusters (K)\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Inercia (SSE)\")\n",
    "plt.title(\"M√©todo del Codo (Elbow Method)\")\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "plt.show()\n"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "sil_scores = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "for k in range(2, 8):\n",
    "    km = KMeans(n_clusters=k, random_state=42)\n",
    "    labels = km.fit_predict(X_sample)\n",
    "    sil_scores[k] = silhouette_score(X_sample, labels)\n",
    "\n",
    "sil_scores\n"
